<div id="pf281e" class="pf w46 h237" data-page-no="281e"><div class="pc pc281e w46 h237"><div class="t m829 xc5 h104 y23a5 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School Lesson Quarterly </div><div class="t mae3 xc hcc y99a ff3 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE CHURCH: ITS STRUGGLES AND VICTORIES </div><div class="t m803 x32 h1c y776 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">GENERAL INTRODUCTION </div><div class="t ma7e x11 h4 y71b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Wonderful is the work which the Lord </div><div class="t ma7 xbd h4 y11ee ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">designs to accomplish through His church, </div><div class="t m9b7 xbd h4 y8ed ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that His name may be glorified.&quot; </div><div class="t m39f x11 h4 y17e3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The church is God&apos;s fortress, His city of </div><div class="t m5f0 x4 h4 y858 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">refuge, which He holds in a revolted world. </div><div class="t m3b9 xbd h4 y7ab ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Any betrayal of the church is treachery to </div><div class="t m12fd xbd h4 y65f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Him who has bought mankind with the </div><div class="t m2da xbd h4 y796 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blood of His only-begotten Son. From the </div><div class="t m119c xbd h4 y13ce ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beginning, faithful souls have constituted </div><div class="t m537 xbd h4 y18a2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the church on earth. In every age the Lord </div><div class="t m723 xbd h4 y46b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has had His watchmen, who have borne a </div><div class="t m6a5 xbd h4 y363 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">faithful testimony to the generation in </div><div class="t m596 xbd h4 y9a3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which they lived. These sentinels gave the </div><div class="t mdcd xbd h4 y11d9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">message of warning; and when they were </div><div class="t m4d5 x4 h4 y798 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">called to lay off their armor, others took up </div><div class="t m203 x4 h4 y8bb ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the work.&quot; </div><div class="t m9db x56 h4 y71b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The church is God&apos;s appointed agency </div><div class="t m7fd x5a h4 y11ee ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the salvation of men. It was organized </div><div class="t mb6c x5a h4 y8ed ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for service, and its mission is to carry the </div><div class="t m128 x5a h4 y17e3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gospel to the world. From the beginning it </div><div class="t mc18 x5a h4 y858 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has been God&apos;s plan that through His </div><div class="t m603 x5a h4 y7ab ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">church shall be reflected to the world His </div><div class="t m62a x5a h4 y13a8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fullness and His sufficiency. The members </div><div class="t mbd8 x5a h4 y77a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the church, those whom He has called </div><div class="t ma42 x5a h4 y126a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">out of darkness into His marvelous light, </div><div class="t m5a3 x5a h4 ydf7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are to show forth His glory. The church is </div><div class="t m345 x5a h4 y2dd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the repository of the riches of the grace of </div><div class="t m4c9 x5a h4 ya04 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ; and through the church will eventu-</div><div class="t m111 x5a h4 ya75 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ally be made manifest, even to &apos;the princi-</div><div class="t m32d x5a h4 y1322 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">palities and powers in heavenly places,&apos; the </div><div class="t m571 x5a h4 y7f7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">final and full display of the love of God.&quot;—</div><div class="t m298 xb0 h30 y3d5 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m1717 xc8 h4 y3d5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 13, 11, 9. </div><div class="t m7f9 x6a h20 y126d ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lesson 1, for April 2, 1955 </div><div class="t m1bf x1d hcc y4ec ff3 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Early Church </div><div class="t m80c x4 h1c y91e ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">MEMORY VERSE: &quot;All power is given unto Me in heaven and in earth. Go ye there-</div><div class="t m17c x18 h1c y66d ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fore, and teach all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father, and of </div><div class="t m576 x18 h1c ydc4 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Son, and of the Holy Ghost: teaching them to observe all things whatsoever </div><div class="t me69 x18 h1c y1750 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I have commanded you: and, lo, I am with you alway, even unto fhe end of </div><div class="t m1117 x18 h1c yb87 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the world.&quot; Matt. 28:18-20. </div><div class="t made x4 h1c y4b8 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">STUDY HELP: &quot;The Desire of Ages,&quot; pages 818-828. </div><div class="t m8df x31 h20 y86a ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY STUDY ASSIGNMENT </div><div class="t m1665 xe h1c y532 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m8c7 x71 h1c y532 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath afternoon: general survey </div><div class="t m5 x1f h1c y1a30 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m2db xb0 h1c y532 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. Questions 8-11. </div><div class="t m3c9 x48 h1c y155d ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the lesson, based on outline. </div><div class="t m5 x79 h1c y1620 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m9cc xb0 h1c y155d ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. Questions 12-15. </div><div class="t ma69 xe h1c y1132 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m2b9 x71 h1c y1132 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction; Questions 1-4. </div><div class="t m5 x68 h1c y16db ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m485 xb0 h1c y1132 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. Read Study Help assignment. </div><div class="t m9b8 xe h1c y4f6 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t ma73 x71 h1c yfbf ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Questions 5-7. </div><div class="t m5 x10 h1c y5ca ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t mfd5 xb0 h1c y4d9 ff2 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. Review entir